reviewText: Great video and lots of valuable information.  I can't wait to watch the first two DVD's.  I highly recommend this video to all beauty professionals.
I finally got around to watching some of this.  I really enjoyed what I have watched so far.  I am thinking about investing in the other esthetic videos.
Love Rita Page. Wish she had a website for her spa though. Can't find it via Google.  Quality cd instruction from Ms. Page, great tips. I bought all her cd's!

If you are an esthetician or want to become one, this video is a must have. This is one of three in the series and each of the videos are excellent. I would recommend all three. Well worth the every penny!
THIS DVD IS ALMOST OR BETTER IN SOME CASE THAN REAL FACIAL CLASSES I TOOK, RECOMMENDED HIGHLY! I DON'T WRITE REVIEWS MUCH BUT THIS FACIAL SERIES VOL.1 THROUGH VOL.3 IS MUST.
